title: Spain’s deputy PM gives up persuading Catalonia not to declare independence
description:
Catalonia's regional President Carles Puigdemont is scheduled to make a speech to congressmen at 6PM local time, that is 16GMT on Tuesday. The speech will focus on the current political situation in the region, and Puigdemont is also likely to declare unilateral independence. 

Subscribe to us on YouTube: https://goo.gl/lP12gA
